    "English": "This autophage is far from working order, but its subcomponents shows the signs of a previous repair attempt. With a few additional tweaks, the work might be completed...<br><br>Repair this component with <span class=\"name name-img\">REPAIR</span>, or use <span class=\"name name-img\">PIN</span> to locate the needed materials.",
